{"tid":1474012,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足可唔可以對中老年人友善啲","createTime":"2019-08-15T04:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T01:50:57.000Z","uid":1495,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e342cb8c2e26c1a416346b2d323f945aa9b6c608","tid":1474012,"uid":1495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:33:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的，其實好多中老年人都好支持我哋<br />\n例如我父母，我老竇甚至係<strong>支持勇武嘅深黃</strong><br />\n但佢每次行過連儂牆，啲手足唔敢派文宣俾佢<br />\n就連85三罷個日去集會，都冇人派嘢俾佢<br />\n佢明白年輕人會對佢呢種大叔有戒心，仲自嘲話可能自己個樣似深藍<br />\n而我老母就話有日放工見到年輕人貼緊文宣，佢八掛睇下貼緊啲咩<br />\n嗰兩位年輕人可能嚇一嚇，然後急急腳走咗<br />\n老母又自嘲話可能因為著住件藍色衫<br />\n直到有日上星期，我老竇又經過連儂牆，終於有手足派嘢俾佢<br />\n佢雖然冇講，但我聽得出佢好開心，覺得自己俾年輕人認可佢係一份子<br />\n<br />\n其實啲中老年人冇惡意，可能好奇同八掛<br />\n希望各位連儂牆手足可以友善地同佢哋傾兩句<br />\n等佢哋接受咗我哋嘅訊息之後向返佢哋朋友、同事宣揚，易過我哋勸呀係咪先<br />\n當然都要注意安全<br />\n<br />\n最後，聽日816 8p.m. 遮打花園有攬炒巴同學界搞嘅集會<br />\n818 2:30p.m. 維園有民陣遊行<br />\n到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3dced19a4802e978f0469a09d5b7a0e0a8a3fa","tid":1474012,"uid":1495,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"我老竇好努力咁喺facebook share 我哋啲資訊俾佢啲朋友同同事睇<br />\n仲成功去啲藍page 度做鍵戰架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847d0de03db1e65532de7dd13c0b2bba0a78b2c2","tid":1474012,"uid":92453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1eeca9929919bdd929693bbd526218fa42d64c9c","tid":1474012,"uid":92453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:52:45.000Z","msg":"感謝樓主兩老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2398b2028beb2d0603f1b3a15f8c82e6f2c3f21b","tid":1474012,"uid":92453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:52:55.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"f262d002be0c81967a65ec73c0a9046dae184e60","tid":1474012,"uid":74663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"我今日去茶記食飯<br />\n對面坐左個中年女人<br />\n隔離個枱係度討論緊政治<br />\n仲諗緊佢係藍定黃既時候<br />\n見到佢手機用緊蘋果日報app<br />\n先知原來係同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e775375d6d2aff28d31209e904223ce58c32741","tid":1474012,"uid":274136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:03:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n長期戰 不氣餒</span></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n唔好意思，阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n香港人重要日程：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>8月15日</strong>：稅局接收工（1200稅務大樓）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月16日</strong>：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月16日</strong>：大家記得撳錢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>8月17日</strong>：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月18日</strong>：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月24日</strong>：觀塘大遊行（1300駿業街球場）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>8月25日</strong>：荃葵青遊街（1400葵青劇院集合）</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位手足，到時見！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ce0fa32c046b46e1d8e5bbbdcb6871cd36738ac5","tid":1474012,"uid":270307,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"db3dced19a4802e978f0469a09d5b7a0e0a8a3fa","tid":1474012,"uid":1495,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"我老竇好努力咁喺facebook share 我哋啲資訊俾佢啲朋友同同事睇<br />\n仲成功去啲藍page 度做鍵戰架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:05:14.000Z","m